sql:
SELECT name
FROM employees
WHERE designation_id = (SELECT designation_id FROM designations WHERE designation_name = 'VP');

SELECT AVG(tax_bracket) AS average_tax_bracket
FROM tax_laws
WHERE country_id = 1;

SELECT tax_bracket, tax_rate
FROM tax_laws
WHERE country_id = 1;

SELECT tax_bracket
FROM tax_laws
WHERE tax_law_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- "places where people work" implies that there should be at least one employee in each group (country, region, profession, and role); 
- "profession" refers to the designation or job title of an employee; 
- "role" refers to the user role in the system.
